millsfield:images_texts:
THANK YOU for your interest in Pan
American's menu covers. We are pleased that you asked
for the complete set and are happy to send them to you.
Many people find that they are beautiful framed; others
keep them among their "souvenirs" as attractive mementos
of a pleasant journey. Whatever your use, we hope you'll
enjoy having them, and that we may have the pleasure of
serving you in the future on a Pan American Clipper flight.
Service Manager
Hawaii
